def is_bathroom_sink(sink: item):
    # Determine if the sink is in the bathroom
    symbol inside_bathroom=exists room: item : is_bathroom(room) and inside(sink, room)
    return inside_bathroom

def has_soap(sink: item):
    # Check if there is soap in the sink
    symbol soap_present=exists soap: item : is_soap(soap) and inside(soap, sink)
    return soap_present

behavior add_soap_to_water(sink: item):
    body:
        if not has_soap(sink):
            foreach soap: item:
                if is_soap(soap) and not visited(soap):
                    observe(soap, "Is it in the bathroom")
        # This condition ensures we attempt observation only if soap is not confirmed to be in the s
ink
        
        bind soap: item where:
            is_soap(soap)
        # Select soap from available items

        # Place soap in the sink with water
        achieve inside(soap, sink)
        # Final mixing action
        achieve clean(sink)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind sink: item where:
            is_sink(sink) and is_bathroom_sink(sink) and has_water(sink)
        # Select the bathroom sink that has water
        add_soap_to_water(sink)
